name: Heavenly Reverberations
description: This creation is a gateway to the final works based on the "GALACTICA 100" artworks, created during the powerful and unforgiving lock-downs, early 2021. It is a mix of Acrylic Painting, Digital Photography, and 3D ray-tracing. It is a unique piece, and part of my artistic research. Each artwork of the Passage to Heaven collection is associated to a Greek letter.
